---
// The FunGen text wordmark lockup: "Fun" in the surrounding ink color,
// "Gen" in the brand teal — matching the pass-delivery email's lockup.
// Text-only span: size/weight/color of "Fun" come from the parent element.
// Same in every locale; use ONLY for brand lockups, never in running prose.
---
<span class="wm">Fun<span class="wm-gen">Gen</span></span>

<style>
  .wm-gen {
    color: var(--teal, #22d3ee);
  }
</style>
